### user register
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName":"Vindhya",
    "lastName":"Enikapally",
    "email":"vindhyaa@gmail.com",
    "password":"vindhya@123",
    "profileImageUrl":"https://example.com/avatars/author.png"
}

###user login
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"vindhya@gmail.com",
    "password":"vindhya@123",
    "role":"USER"
}

